{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"## Root Cause","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734491354Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734497996Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"When the daemon restarts (or crashes), `FailStaleRuns()` marks in-flight runs as failed in SQLite, but **never resets the corresponding beads tasks from `in_progress` back to `open`**. Since `ListReady` only returns tasks with `status == \"open\"`, these orphaned `in_progress` tasks become permanently invisible to the orchestrator — even though no run is actually processing them.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734501423Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734517714Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"The scenario: 4 tasks were open, the orchestrator claimed them (setting status to `in_progress`), then the daemon restarted. After restart, `ListReady` returns 0 tasks (all are `in_progress`), so `cloche orchestrate` reports \"No ready work found\". Meanwhile `bd list` shows them because it displays all non-closed tasks.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.7345212Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734529205Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"## Fix","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734532712Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734535938Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"Three changes:","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734539144Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734546488Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"1. **`ports.TaskTracker` interface** (`internal/ports/tracker.go`): Added `RecoverStaleTasks(ctx) (int, error)` method to reset orphaned `in_progress` tasks.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734549864Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734557288Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"2. **Beads adapter** (`internal/adapters/beads/tracker.go`): Implemented `RecoverStaleTasks` — scans for `in_progress` tasks and appends status updates resetting them to `open`.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734560645Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734567989Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"3. **Daemon startup** (`cmd/cloched/main.go`): Added `orch.RecoverAll()` call before `TriggerAll()`, which iterates all registered projects and calls `RecoverStaleTasks` on each tracker. The `Orchestrator.RecoverAll` method is in `internal/orchestrator/orchestrator.go`.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734571465Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T02:59:34.734576024Z"}
